This show was one of the funniest of its season. The characters are all likable and adorable. Maki has to be one of the nuttiest girls ever, but she's very endearing. And Riko is a master at digging her own grave deeper and deeper. A must watch for comedy lovers. It's kind of a funnier School Rumble/Azumanga Daioh.

Subs are from Commie.
